outputs.output_descr: Under its new Strategic Plan, Amkeni Wakenya Civil Society Democratic Governance Facility is focusing on supporting CSOs to implement the new Constitution in three thematic areas: Access to Justice, Devolution and Human Rights.

project_descr: Supporting CSOs working in the areas of democracy, human rights, access to justice, good governance and the integration of a human rights-based approach and gender mainstreaming in governance processes and reforms in Kenya
